{"title":"早行","authors":["石太瑞"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":1,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"早行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石太瑞（苗族）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡未打鸣，鸟未啼叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫夜雾把群山笼罩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水在打着呼噜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村在静静睡觉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有驾驶员不知疲劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着夜色行车赶早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别温暖的小站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑进大山的怀抱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南来的，电光闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北去的，四轮呼啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见面相互多亲热，——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借车灯对话，用鸣笛问好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为四化建设抢速度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨不能两天路程一天到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日奔多少里？山高水远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜唱什么歌？多拉快跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一坡晨雾随风散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一天曙光铺满道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往后看哟，险峰已过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝前奔哟，山欢水笑。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}